## Motivation

This guide summarizes the overall motivation behind the static site generator that Mike has used for several websites:

* https://ml4health.github.io/2017/
* https://ml4health.github.io/2018/
* https://www.cs.tufts.edu/research/ml/

Also used by Mike for courses

* BDL: https://www.cs.tufts.edu/comp/150BDL/2018f/
* Intro ML: https://www.cs.tufts.edu/comp/136/2021s/
* Statistical Pattern Recognition: https://www.cs.tufts.edu/comp/136/2021s/

This website template has been even used by other people!

* https://mlpcp21.github.io/index.html

## Documentation

* Pelican static site generator: https://docs.getpelican.com/en/latest/

* README of our Tufts ML website: https://github.com/tufts-ml/tufts_ml_website/
